This allows to group multiple monochromatic LEDs into a multicolor
LED, e.g. RGB LEDs.

Signed-off-by: Jean-Jacques Hiblot <jjhiblot@traphandler.com>
Reviewed-by: Rob Herring <robh@kernel.org>
